<td>$10-30/month</td>
<td>90-95%</td>
<td>High</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Professional transcription (Rev, GoTranscript)</td>
<td>$1-2/minute</td>
<td>99%+</td>
<td>Highest</td>
</tr>
<tr>
